      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute dream of a car, and honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve spent more time babying this beauty than I care to admit\u2014it\u2019s spotless inside and out, runs like a charm, and has been garage-kept since day one. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
