      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence that must be seen to be fully appreciated. This vehicle remains in absolute showroom condition, having been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior finish is flawless, retaining a deep, mirror-like luster with zero rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings, further enhanced by a multi-stage professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains taut and supple without a single crease or sign of bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by custom-fit liners since day one. Every feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate driver-assistance tech, operates with factory-new precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history with every interval performed ahead of schedule by master technicians. This is a collector-grade specimen that offers the exact tactile and visual experience of a brand-new vehicle. I welcome and encourage independent pre-purchase inspections to confirm that this car meets the highest possible standards of preservation.",
